{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879539422,"sessionID":"ses_285582da9ffeVekszX7tvUptvr","part":{"id":"prt_d7aab4a54001JherhPOklhp8zW","messageID":"msg_d7aa855eb001Xpn97MCmgwhziV","sessionID":"ses_285582da9ffeVekszX7tvUptvr","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-738516d2883f468faa7da111cb1aefca","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-027/tasks.md","content":"# AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient |\n| Module | `sdk-python` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed]\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Exception Hierarchy (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Implement `AgentCubeError` base exception class\n  - Purpose: Define base exception for all AgentCube SDK errors\n  - File: `agentcube/exceptions.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.exceptions import AgentCubeError; raise AgentCubeError('test')\"`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2**: Implement `CommandExecutionError` exception with exit_code, stderr, command\n  - Purpose: Exception for non-zero exit code from remote command execution\n  - File: `agentcube/exceptions.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.exceptions import CommandExecutionError; e = CommandExecutionError(1, 'err', 'cmd'); print(e.exit_code)\"`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3**: Implement `SessionError` exception subclass\n  - Purpose: Exception for control plane session operations\n  - File: `agentcube/exceptions.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.exceptions import SessionError; print(isinstance(SessionError(), AgentCubeError))\"`\n\n- [ ] **T1.4**: Implement `DataPlaneError` exception subclass\n  - Purpose: Exception for data plane communication errors\n  - File: `agentcube/exceptions.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.exceptions import DataPlaneError; print(isinstance(DataPlaneError(), AgentCubeError))\"`\n\n### Phase 2: Utility Modules (ST-2)\n\n- [ ] **T2.1**: Implement `create_session()` helper in `utils/http.py`\n  - Purpose: Create requests.Session with HTTPAdapter for connection pooling\n  - File: `agentcube/utils/http.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.utils.http import create_session; s = create_session(); print(type(s))\"`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2**: Implement `read_token_from_file()` helper in `utils/utils.py`\n  - Purpose: Read Kubernetes service account token from `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token`\n  - File: `agentcube/utils/utils.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_utils.py::test_read_token_from_file -v`\n\n- [ ] **T2.3**: Implement `get_logger()` helper in `utils/log.py`\n  - Purpose: Return configured logger instance for SDK operations\n  - File: `agentcube/utils/log.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.utils.log import get_logger; log = get_logger('test'); print(type(log))\"`\n\n- [ ] **T2.4**: Create `agentcube/utils/__init__.py` with exports\n  - Purpose: Export utility functions from utils package\n  - File: `agentcube/utils/__init__.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.utils import create_session, read_token_from_file, get_logger; print('OK')\"`\n\n### Phase 3: ControlPlaneClient Implementation (ST-3)\n\n- [ ] **T3.1**: Implement `ControlPlaneClient.__init__` with base_url, timeout, connect_timeout\n  - Purpose: Initialize HTTP client for Workload Manager API\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestControlPlaneClientInit -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.2**: Implement `ControlPlaneClient` auth token resolution logic\n  - Purpose: Resolve auth_token from arg or `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token`\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestAuthTokenResolution -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.3**: Implement `ControlPlaneClient` Authorization header when token present\n  - Purpose: Set `Authorization: Bearer {token}` header on session\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestBearerAuthHeader -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.4**: Implement `ControlPlaneClient._resolve_url()` helper\n  - Purpose: Resolve workload_manager_url from arg or `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` env var\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestURLResolution -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.5**: Implement `ControlPlaneClient.create_session()` method\n  - Purpose: POST `{base_url}/v1/code-interpreter` with JSON body name, namespace, ttl, metadata\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestCreateSession -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.6**: Implement `ControlPlaneClient.create_session()` return sessionId extraction\n  - Purpose: Return `data[\"sessionId\"]` or raise ValueError if absent\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestCreateSession::test_create_session_missing_session_id -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.7**: Implement `ControlPlaneClient.delete_session()` method\n  - Purpose: DELETE `{base_url}/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{session_id}`\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestDeleteSession -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.8**: Implement `ControlPlaneClient.delete_session()` 404 handling\n  - Purpose: Return True on 404, log and return False on other failures\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestDeleteSession::test_delete_session_404_returns_true -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.9**: Implement `ControlPlaneClient.close()` method\n  - Purpose: Close the HTTP session connection pool\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestClose -v`\n\n### Phase 4: CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient Implementation (ST-4)\n\n- [ ] **T4.1**: Implement `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient.__init__` with session_id, base_url, timeout\n  - Purpose: Initialize data plane client with session header setup\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py::TestDataPlaneClientInit -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.2**: Implement data plane session header `x-agentcube-session-id`\n  - Purpose: Set lowercase `x-agentcube-session-id` header on all requests\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py::TestSessionHeader -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.3**: Implement data plane `base_url` construction via `urljoin`\n  - Purpose: Build base_url from router_url + `/v1/namespaces/{ns}/code-interpreters/{cr_name}/invocations/`\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py::TestBaseURLConstruction -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.4**: Implement `execute_command()` method\n  - Purpose: POST `api/execute` with JSON `{\"command\": [...], \"timeout\": \"<n>s\"}`\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py::TestExecuteCommand -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.5**: Implement `execute_command()` read timeout buffer logic\n  - Purpose: Set read timeout to `timeout_value + 2.0` seconds to avoid ReadTimeout before PicoD returns exit 124\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py::TestExecuteCommand::test_execute_command_timeout_buffer -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.6**: Implement `execute_command()` non-zero exit handling\n  - Purpose: Raise `CommandExecutionError(exit_code, stderr, command)` when exit_code != 0\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py::TestExecuteCommand::test_execute_command_nonzero_exit -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.7**: Implement `write_file()` method\n  - Purpose: POST `api/files` with base64 content, path, mode `\"0644\"`\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py::TestWriteFile -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.8**: Implement `upload_file()` method\n  - Purpose: POST multipart to `api/files` with `files={'file': ...}`, `data={'path', 'mode'}` and session header\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py::TestUploadFile -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.9**: Implement `download_file()` method\n  - Purpose: GET `api/files/{clean_path}` with `stream=True`\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py::TestDownloadFile -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.10**: Implement `list_files()` method\n  - Purpose: GET `api/files` with query param `path`\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py::TestListFiles -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.11**: Implement `close()` method for data plane client\n  - Purpose: Close the HTTP session\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py::TestClose -v`\n\n### Phase 5: CodeInterpreterClient Implementation (ST-5)\n\n- [ ] **T5.1**: Implement `CodeInterpreterClient.__init__` with name, namespace, ttl, workload_manager_url, router_url, auth_token, verbose, session_id\n  - Purpose: Initialize main client with all configuration parameters\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestCodeInterpreterClientInit -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.2**: Implement Router URL required validation\n  - Purpose: Raise ValueError if router_url not provided via arg and ROUTER_URL env var\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestRouterURLRequired -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.3**: Implement `_resolve_router_url()` helper\n  - Purpose: Resolve router_url from arg or `ROUTER_URL` env var\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestRouterURLResolution -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.4**: Implement session reuse logic when session_id provided\n  - Purpose: Skip create_session call when session_id argument is provided\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestSessionReuse -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.5**: Implement session creation via ControlPlaneClient\n  - Purpose: Call cp_client.create_session when no session_id provided\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestSessionCreation -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.6**: Implement `_init_data_plane()` private method\n  - Purpose: Initialize CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient with session_id and router_url\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestDataPlaneInit -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.7**: Implement data plane init failure cleanup\n  - Purpose: Log warning, call delete_session(session_id), set session_id to None, re-raise on data plane init failure\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestDataPlaneInitFailureCleanup -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.8**: Implement `__enter__()` context manager method\n  - Purpose: Return self for context manager usage\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestContextManager -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.9**: Implement `__exit__()` context manager method\n  - Purpose: Call stop() on context exit (with or without exception)\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestContextManager::test_context_manager_calls_stop -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.10**: Implement `execute_command()` delegation method\n  - Purpose: Delegate to dp_client.execute_command with command and timeout\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestExecuteCommand -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.11**: Implement `run_code()` method for Python execution\n  - Purpose: Write timestamped .py file via write_file, execute python3 <file> via execute_command\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestRunCode -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.12**: Implement `run_code()` language detection (python/py/python3)\n  - Purpose: Check language is python, py, or python3 before Python execution path\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestRunCode::test_run_code_python_language -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.13**: Implement `write_file()` delegation method\n  - Purpose: Delegate to dp_client.write_file\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestWriteFile -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.14**: Implement `upload_file()` delegation method\n  - Purpose: Delegate to dp_client.upload_file\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestUploadFile -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.15**: Implement `download_file()` delegation method\n  - Purpose: Delegate to dp_client.download_file\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestDownloadFile -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.16**: Implement `list_files()` delegation method\n  - Purpose: Delegate to dp_client.list_files\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestListFiles -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.17**: Implement `stop()` method\n  - Purpose: Close data-plane session, delete control-plane session if session_id was set, close control plane HTTP session\n  - File: `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py::TestStop -v`\n\n### Phase 6: Package Exports (ST-6)\n\n- [ ] **T6.1**: Create `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` with exports\n  - Purpose: Export ControlPlaneClient, CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient\n  - File: `agentcube/clients/__init__.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.clients import ControlPlaneClient, CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient; print('OK')\"`\n\n- [ ] **T6.2**: Update `agentcube/__init__.py` with public exports\n  - Purpose: Export CodeInterpreterClient, AgentRuntimeClient from top-level package\n  - File: `agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube import CodeInterpreterClient; print('OK')\"`\n\n- [ ] **T6.3**: Update `agentcube/exceptions.py` exports\n  - Purpose: Ensure all exception classes are importable\n  - File: `agentcube/exceptions.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.exceptions import AgentCubeError, CommandExecutionError, SessionError, DataPlaneError; print('OK')\"`\n\n### Phase 7: ControlPlaneClient Unit Tests (ST-7)\n\n- [ ] **T7.1**: Test ControlPlaneClient init with default timeout values\n  - Purpose: Verify default read timeout 120s, connect timeout 5.0s\n  - File: `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestControlPlaneClientInit::test_init_default_timeout -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.2**: Test ControlPlaneClient init with custom timeout\n  - Purpose: Verify custom timeout values are stored\n  - File: `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestControlPlaneClientInit::test_init_custom_timeout -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.3**: Test auth token from explicit argument\n  - Purpose: Verify token from auth_token arg sets Bearer header\n  - File: `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::TestAuthTokenResolution::test_auth_token_explicit -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.4**: Test auth token from file fallback\n  - Purpose: Verify token read from service account file when arg omitted\n  - File: `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n  - Verific