ify CommandExecutionError raised on failure\n  - File: `tests/test_integration.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_integration.py::TestCommandError -v`\n\n- [ ] **T10.5**: Test session reuse across operations\n  - Purpose: Verify session_id reused across multiple operations\n  - File: `tests/test_integration.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_integration.py::TestSessionReuse -v`\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nPhase 1 (Exceptions) ────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT1.1 (AgentCubeError) ──┬── T1.2 (CommandExecutionError)\n                        ├── T1.3 (SessionError)\n                        └── T1.4 (DataPlaneError)\n\nPhase 2 (Utilities) ────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT2.1 (create_session) ──┬── T3.1 (ControlPlaneClient init)\n                        └── T4.1 (DataPlaneClient init)\nT2.2 (read_token) ──────┬── T3.2 (auth token resolution)\nT2.3 (get_logger) ──────┬── T5.1 (CodeInterpreterClient init)\nT2.4 (utils init) ──────┬── T6.1 (clients init)\n\nPhase 3 (ControlPlaneClient) ────────────────────────────────────────\nT3.1 (init) ──┬── T3.2 (auth token)\n              ├── T3.3 (Bearer header)\n              ├── T3.4 (URL resolution)\n              └── T3.5 (create_session)\n                         └── T3.6 (sessionId extraction)\n              ├── T3.7 (delete_session)\n                         └── T3.8 (404 handling)\n              └── T3.9 (close)\n\nPhase 4 (DataPlaneClient) ────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT4.1 (init) ──┬── T4.2 (session header)\n              ├── T4.3 (base_url construction)\n              ├── T4.4 (execute_command)\n                         ├── T4.5 (timeout buffer)\n                         └── T4.6 (non-zero exit)\n              ├── T4.7 (write_file)\n              ├── T4.8 (upload_file)\n              ├── T4.9 (download_file)\n              ├── T4.10 (list_files)\n              └── T4.11 (close)\n\nPhase 5 (CodeInterpreterClient) ────────────────────────────────────────\nT5.1 (init) ──┬── T5.2 (Router URL required)\n              ├── T5.3 (router URL resolution)\n              ├── T5.4 (session reuse)\n              ├── T5.5 (session creation)\n              ├── T5.6 (data plane init)\n                         └── T5.7 (failure cleanup)\n              ├── T5.8 (__enter__)\n              ├── T5.9 (__exit__)\n              ├── T5.10-T5.16 (delegation methods)\n              └── T5.17 (stop)\n\nPhase 3-5 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT3.1-T3.9 ────┬── T7.1-T7.12 (ControlPlane tests)\nT4.1-T4.11 ───┬── T8.1-T8.14 (DataPlane tests)\nT5.1-T5.17 ───┬── T9.1-T9.21 (CodeInterpreter tests)\n\nPhase 6 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT1.1-T1.4 ────┬── T6.3 (exceptions exports)\nT3.1-T4.11 ───┬── T6.1 (clients exports)\nT5.1-T5.17 ───┬── T6.2 (top-level exports)\n\nPhase 7-9 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT7.1-T7.12 ───┬── T10.1-T10.5 (integration)\nT8.1-T8.14 ───┬── T10.1-T10.5 (integration)\nT9.1-T9.21 ───┬── T10.1-T10.5 (integration)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| Phase 1 | `python -c \"from agentcube.exceptions import *; print('OK')\"` |\n| Phase 2 | `pytest tests/test_utils.py -v` |\n| Phase 3 | `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py -v` |\n| Phase 4 | `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py -v` |\n| Phase 5 | `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py -v` |\n| Phase 6 | `python -c \"from agentcube import CodeInterpreterClient; from agentcube.clients import *; print('OK')\"` |\n| Phase 7 | `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py -v` |\n| Phase 8 | `pytest tests/test_data_plane.py -v` |\n| Phase 9 | `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter.py -v` |\n| Phase 10 | `pytest tests/test_integration.py -v` |\n| All Tests | `pytest tests/ -v` |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreterClient.__init__` with `name`, `namespace`, `ttl`, `workload_manager_url`, `router_url`, `auth_token`, `verbose`, `session_id`\n- [ ] Router URL required: raises `ValueError` if missing via arg and env\n- [ ] Context manager: `__enter__` returns self, `__exit__` calls `stop()`\n- [ ] Session reuse: skips `create_session` when `session_id` provided\n- [ ] Data plane init failure cleanup: deletes session, logs warning, re-raises\n- [ ] `execute_command`: JSON body `{\"command\": [...], \"timeout\": \"<n>s\"}`, read timeout buffer `+2.0`\n- [ ] Non-zero exit: raises `CommandExecutionError(exit_code, stderr, command)`\n- [ ] `run_code`: writes timestamped `.py` file, executes via `python3`\n- [ ] `write_file`: base64 content, mode `\"0644\"`\n- [ ] `upload_file`: multipart POST with `x-agentcube-session-id`\n- [ ] `download_file`: GET with `stream=True`\n- [ ] `list_files`: GET with query `path`\n- [ ] Session header: `x-agentcube-session-id` on all data plane requests\n- [ ] Control plane: `POST` `/v1/code-interpreter`, `DELETE` `/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{id}`\n- [ ] `delete_session`: 404 returns `True`, other failures log and return `False`\n- [ ] Auth token: explicit arg or `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token`\n- [ ] `Authorization: Bearer {token}` header when token present\n- [ ] Default timeouts: read `120s`, connect `5.0s`\n- [ ] Exception hierarchy: `AgentCubeError`, `CommandExecutionError`, `SessionError`, `DataPlaneError`\n\n---\n\n## File Changes Summary\n\n| File | Action | Lines | Description |\n|------|--------|-------|-------------|\n| `agentcube/exceptions.py` | Create | ~40 | Exception hierarchy classes |\n| `agentcube/utils/http.py` | Create | ~30 | HTTP session creation helper |\n| `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | Create | ~20 | Token file reader helper |\n| `agentcube/utils/log.py` | Create | ~15 | Logger configuration helper |\n| `agentcube/utils/__init__.py` | Create | ~5 | Utils package exports |\n| `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | Create | ~100 | ControlPlaneClient implementation |\n| `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | Create | ~150 | CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient implementation |\n| `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` | Create | ~5 | Clients package exports |\n| `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | Create | ~200 | CodeInterpreterClient implementation |\n| `agentcube/__init__.py` | Modify | ~10 | Top-level package exports |\n| `tests/test_utils.py` | Create | ~50 | Utility module tests |\n| `tests/test_control_plane.py` | Create | ~150 | ControlPlaneClient unit tests |\n| `tests/test_data_plane.py` | Create | ~200 | DataPlaneClient unit tests |\n| `tests/test_code_interpreter.py` | Create | ~250 | CodeInterpreterClient unit tests |\n| `tests/test_integration.py` | Create | ~100 | Integration tests |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### Session Header Convention\n\nAll data plane requests use lowercase header name:\n```python\nheaders = {\"x-agentcube-session-id\": session_id}\n```\n\n### Timeout Buffer Strategy\n\nExecute command read timeout includes buffer to avoid `ReadTimeout` before PicoD returns exit 124:\n```python\nread_timeout = timeout_value + 2.0  # 2 second buffer\n```\n\n### Base URL Construction\n\nData plane base_url is constructed using `urljoin`:\n```python\nbase_url = urljoin(router_url, f\"/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/code-interpreters/{cr_name}/invocations/\")\n```\n\n### Auth Token Resolution Order\n\n1. Explicit `auth_token` argument\n2. Kubernetes service account file: `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token`\n\n### Default Timeout Values\n\n| Timeout | Value | Purpose |\n|---------|-------|---------|\n| Read timeout | 120s | HTTP response read timeout |\n| Connect timeout | 5.0s | HTTP connection establishment |\n\n### File Write Format\n\n```python\n{\n    \"path\": \"/workspace/file.py\",\n    \"content\": base64.b64encode(content_bytes).decode(),\n    \"mode\": \"0644\"\n}\n```\n\n### Execute Command Format\n\n```python\n{\n    \"command\": [\"python3\", \"/workspace/file.py\"],\n    \"timeout\": \"30s\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: Exceptions | T1.1-T1.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 2: Utilities | T2.1-T2.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 3: ControlPlaneClient | T3.1-T3.9 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 4: DataPlaneClient | T4.1-T4.11 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 5: CodeInterpreterClient | T5.1-T5.17 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 6: Package Exports | T6.1-T6.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 7: ControlPlane Tests | T7.1-T7.12 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 8: DataPlane Tests | T8.1-T8.14 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 9: CodeInterpreter Tests | T9.1-T9.21 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 10: Integration | T10.1-T10.5 | Pending | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/80 tasks)**\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Design: `changes/AR-027/design.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md`\n- `python-sdk/design.md` — AgentCube Python SDK design\n- `python-sdk/spec.md` — AgentCube Python SDK specification"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-027/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-027/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775879539374,"end":1775879539418}}}}
